Name: dlg.set_groupbox_checked
Desc: Set the initial state of the GroupBox's checkbox to show/hide. In case of showing, the initial state of the checkbox is checked
Arg1: name
- A String specifying the name of the component in which will be used for setting the state of its checkbox to show/hide.
